```plantuml
@startuml KMuthumala_ESP32-BLE-Beaconing

actor User
participant "ESP32" as ESP
participant "BLE Devices" as BLE
participant "WiFi Network" as WiFi
participant "MQTT Broker" as MQTT

User -> ESP: Start System
ESP -> WiFi: Connect to WiFi
WiFi -> ESP: Connection Established

loop Continuous Scanning
    ESP -> BLE: Scan for BLE devices
    BLE -> ESP: Return MAC addresses and RSSI
end

ESP -> MQTT: Connect to MQTT Broker
MQTT -> ESP: Connection Established

loop Data Transmission
    ESP -> MQTT: Publish BLE data in JSON format
    MQTT -> ESP: Acknowledge Receipt
end

ESP -> MQTT: Subscribe to command topic
MQTT -> ESP: Incoming Commands

alt WiFi Connection Lost
    ESP -> WiFi: Reconnect to WiFi
    WiFi -> ESP: Reconnection Successful
end

alt MQTT Connection Lost
    ESP -> MQTT: Reconnect to MQTT Broker
    MQTT -> ESP: Reconnection Successful
end

@enduml
```